Philippines May Bid Out Contract to Convert Nuclear Power Plant

-- B y   J o e l   G u i n t o
-- 
2011-08-23T03:03:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/philippines-may-bid-out-contract-to-convert-nuclear-power-plant.html
The  Philippines  may bid out a
contract to convert a mothballed nuclear power plant into a
facility that will run using either coal or gas, Energy
Secretary Rene Almendras said in  Manila  today.  “We’re studying whether it’s cheaper to convert it to
either coal or to natural gas,” Almendras said in an interview.
“Many groups will be interested.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
